immediately after waking up.

rows.label: kizunainn061_msg0002

at the Cliffs of Mors in the evening,
we'll probably see a beautiful sunset[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: kizunainn061_msg0003
rows.name: You want to go, don't you[ML:Dash ] Right?
